{"parse":{"title":"Observations on the Feeling of the Beautiful and Sublime","pageid":1519272,"revid":844973562,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption style=\"font-style:italic;padding-bottom:0.2em;\">Observations on the Feeling of the Beautiful and Sublime <span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Observations+on+the+Feeling+of+the+Beautiful+and+Sublime&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BImmanuel+Kant%5D%5D\"></span></caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Observations_on_the_Feeling_of_the_Beautiful_and_Sublime_(German_edition).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Observations on the Feeling of the Beautiful and Sublime (German edition).jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/78/Observations_on_the_Feeling_of_the_Beautiful_and_Sublime_%28German_edition%29.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"301\" data-file-width=\"180\" data-file-height=\"301\" /></a><div>The German edition</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Immanuel_Kant\" title=\"Immanuel Kant\">Immanuel Kant</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original&#160;title</th><td>\n<i>Beobachtungen \u00fcber das Gef\u00fchl des Sch\u00f6nen und Erhabenen</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nGerman</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Subject</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Aesthetics\" title=\"Aesthetics\">Aesthetics</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Published</th><td>\n1764</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Media&#160;type</th><td>\nPrint</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"vertical-navbox nowraplinks plainlist\" style=\"float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;font-size:88%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-top:0.4em;line-height:1.2em\">Part of <a href=\"